text: Telemundo was a German pay television owned by NBCUniversal International Networks. The channel was available on Premiere and Sky. The channel launched on 21 December 1997. The channel aired shows from the US Telemundo dubbed in German. However, the channel closed on 25 February 2010 with content moving to NBC, which later closed on 22 February 2023.
